One of the sinks in my house broke.
Well, the sink handle broke off.
So... I don't know how to fix this.

Maybe I don't quite understand what exactly happened. But, just buy new! Replace sink handle is not to hard.
Unfortunately, the sink is old, and I don't think it'll be possible to find a matching replacement.
It's one of those two-sink setups.
So having two different sinks next to each other might not... look very good.
I guess we could hire someone to install two new ones. But jeez, I wish I didn't have to.
